Package com.bmd.jrt.builder

Classes and interfaces related to routine builders.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    RoutineBuilder
    Interface defining a builder of routine objects.
    RoutineChannelBuilder
    Interface extending a builder of routine objects.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    RoutineConfiguration
    Class storing the routine configuration.
    RoutineConfigurationBuilder
    Class implementing a builder of routine configurations.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    RoutineBuilder.RunnerType
    Synchronous runner type enumeration.
    RoutineChannelBuilder.DataOrder
    Enumeration defining how data are ordered inside a channel.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    InputDeadLockException
    Exception indicating that no room in the input channel buffer became available before the timeout elapsed.
    OutputDeadLockException
    Exception indicating that no room in the output channel buffer became available before the timeout elapsed.
